<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢١٨٣ - ر م ح]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رمَحَ يَرمَح، رَمْحًا، فهو رامِح، والمفعول مرموح <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• رمَح الفَرسُ ونحوُه:</span> عدا وجَرى.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• رمَح فلانٌ فلانًا:</span> طَعَنه بالرُّمْح <span class="c1">"رَجُلٌ رامِحٌ: ذو رُمْح"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>